{
  "stem": "3100.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So they did her a favor and, and, and they shot her.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now every time I speak about this story, I gain, literally, more respect because not everybody could do that.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was the instinct of a mother not to give up a baby infant.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, of course, that was the end of her.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When we were liberated and, of course, I became a translator with the Russians--",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "An interpreter.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "An interpreter.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So, after a month or so of being liberated, I found out that my wife was there left with 12 other women. 12 women were left from, from maybe 50,000 or 60,000 women throughout the years.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What they--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Uh huh.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were called the shedim, or the devils.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because after what they went through in Majdanek, in Auschwitz, and what they went through in Bergen-Belsen, and what they went through to burn the bodies in Trawniki-- because there was, I understand, in 1943 was one bloody Wednesday.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Where the three camps.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "One camps they finished up over 18,000 Jews in Majdanek, 18,000 Jews in Poniatowa.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "By the way, where my brother-in-law was taken to Poniatowa, and presumably he was killed on that day in Poniatowa and, of course, about 10,000 people in Trawniki.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they left 120 men in Trawniki.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they took a transport of 40 women to Trawniki right after-- a day or two after this bloody Wednesday.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And, of course, my wife was one of those--",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--in that transport that survived.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So there were 12 women that kept themselves together.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In those 12 women, among those 12 women, was also those two girls that I remember, [?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Havalen ?] and [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Simala ?].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they were cousins to my brother-in-law.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there's where I received the news about my, my, d-- my sister.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
